  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"MU-GEN NO TOU\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is said that a famous wizard built this tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It can be climbed infinitely, and no one has ever reached the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's climb the tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -When the time limit is up, you will be thrown out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Touch the door to proceed to the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  -Time is added when you go up to the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -The inside of the tower is randomly generated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the items that can be picked up in the tower to get through the various obstacles efficiently.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"MU-GEN NO TOU\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is said that a famous wizard built this tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It can be climbed infinitely, and no one has ever reached the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's climb the tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -When the time limit is up, you will be thrown out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Touch the door to proceed to the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  -Time is added when you go up to the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -The inside of the tower is randomly generated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the items that can be picked up in the tower to get through the various obstacles efficiently.</p>",
